original_text: And the manna ceased on the morrow after they had eaten of the old corn of the land; neither had the children of Israel manna any more; but they did eat of the fruit of the land of Canaan that year.
korean_text: 또 그 땅의 소산물을 먹은 다음 날에 만나가 그쳤으니 이스라엘 사람들이 다시는 만나를 얻지 못하였고 그 해에 가나안 땅의 소출을 먹었더라

sentences.original_text: And the manna ceased on the morrow
after they had eaten of the old corn of the land
sentences.korean_translation: 그들이 그 땅의 묵은 곡식을 먹은 후에

sentences.original_text: neither had the children of Israel manna any more
sentences.korean_translation: 이스라엘 자손들이 더 이상 만나를 얻지 못했으며

sentences.original_text: but they did eat of the fruit of the land
of the land of Canaan that year
